snippet.title: Plutonium Mario 64 (Savestateless)
snippet.description:
Hello! This is a playthrough of Plutonium Mario 64 by usernamesarespiders.

This hack is good, the levels are big which made it fun to move around in. (Besides c8, I really didn't like that level.) I had trouble finding the cap stages and found them near the end of the hack.

Streamed Live at: https://www.twitch.tv/ozsef
My Romhacking.com Page: https://romhacking.com/user/Ozsef
